(1956, 1, '2014-06-10 14:56:52', '2014-06-10 07:56:52', 'At ICEAT we pride ourselves on the excellence of our recruitment solutions. By utilizing our global reach we have consistently demonstrated our ability to attract the very highest caliber of teachers to the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia.\r\n\r\nBy not only attracting the best, brightest and most highly qualified teachers, but also by working hard to keep them, we are able to provide a complete and stable recruitment solution to our clients.\r\n\r\nOver the years we have listened to our staff, and through our unrivaled retention strategies, we now consistently excel in keeping them, with retention rates far in excess of industry norms in the Kingdom. \r\n', 'Recruitment Solutions', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', 'recruitment-solutions', '', '', '2014-06-20 08:30:30', '2014-06-20 01:30:30', '', 1954, 'http://sfr-creative.com/?page_id=1956', 1, 'page', '', 0),
