(1973, 1, '2014-06-10 15:03:10', '2014-06-10 08:03:10', 'Together with our national and international partners we work hard to combine best practices in the world of education with our clear understanding of local needs. In so doing we at ICEAT are continually striving to improve the world-class management solutions provided to our education and training clients in the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia.\r\n\r\nFrom our unparalleled human-resources systems and procedures to our performance management, our understanding of the detailed administrative demands of large-scale education providers, and our knowledge and experience delivering assessment eLearning and professional development solutions, we provide the very highest quality in education management.', 'Turnkey Solutions', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', 'turnkey-solutions', '', '', '2014-06-20 08:30:31', '2014-06-20 01:30:31', '', 1954, 'http://sfr-creative.com/?page_id=1973', 6, 'page', '', 0),
