(1977, 1, '2014-06-10 15:03:57', '2014-06-10 08:03:57', 'At ICEAT we believe our companies greatest resource is our employees, and our nations greatest resource is our people. That is why we are so passionately committed to creating excellence in education for all in the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia.\r\n\r\nBy attracting the very best educators from around the world, and from within the Kingdom, we have worked hard to develop a team capable of contributing in a meaningful way to the education landscape in the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia.\r\n\r\nWith expertise in curriculum development and delivery, teaching methodology, syllabi design, educational publications and blended learning, we have sought to build a team with the knowledge and expertise to insure excellence in education. By combining this knowledge with our understanding of local needs, we are continually working to create excellence in education in the Kingdom', 'Learning Solutions', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', 'learning-solutions', '', '', '2014-06-20 08:30:30', '2014-06-20 01:30:30', '', 1954, 'http://sfr-creative.com/?page_id=1977', 2, 'page', '', 0),
