(1988, 1, '2014-06-10 15:06:28', '2014-06-10 08:06:28', 'In our experience assessment and testing have proved of paramount importance in the success and continual improvement and development of the programs we have been involved with.\r\n\r\nThe right testing and assessment model can ensure all students are placed at the correct level throughout the program, optimising learning outcomes with materials matched to and appropriate for their language needs. This has continual proven to be an essential component for a successful program, and a vital key to the constant improvement of your program.\r\n\r\nOur teams knowledge and expertise regarding the assessment and testing solutions available, the logistical demands and considerations of large scale testing and the key considerations when selecting testing and assessment materials to utilize, has and will continue to prove essential to our clients.', 'Assessment / Testing Solutions', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', 'assessment-testing-solutions', '', '', '2014-06-20 08:30:30', '2014-06-20 01:30:30', '', 1954, 'http://sfr-creative.com/?page_id=1988', 4, 'page', '', 0),
