(2113, 1, '2014-06-10 17:52:26', '2014-06-10 10:52:26', 'At ICEAT we believe our companies greatest resource is our employees, and our nations greatest resource is our people. That is why we are so passionately committed to creating excellence in education for all in the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia.\r\n\r\nBy attracting the very best educators from around the world, and from within the Kingdom, we have worked hard to develop a team capable of contributing in a meaningful way to the education landscape in the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia.\r\n\r\nWith expertise in curriculum development and delivery, teaching methodology, syllabi design, educational publications and blended learning, we have sought to build a team with the knowledge and expertise to insure excellence in education. By combining this knowledge with our understanding of local needs, we are continually working to create excellence in education in the Kingdom', 'Learning Solutions', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1977-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-10 17:52:26', '2014-06-10 10:52:26', '', 1977, 'http://sfr-creative.com/1977-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(2114, 1, '2014-06-10 17:53:38', '2014-06-10 10:53:38', 'We at ICEAT have played a key role at King Saud University’s Preparatory Year Program, the Kingdom’s most prestigious and ambitious foundation project and the worlds largest English language program, since 2009. Through this role we have gained invaluable experience in the challenges involved with the successful delivery of preparatory year programs in Saudi Arabia. This experience has and will continue to prove invaluable to our partners.\r\n \r\nWe have learnt invaluable lessons, we have witnessed first hand the highs and lows and we have observed the strategies that were successful and those that were not. This has enabled our highly qualified and internationally experienced team to gain comprehensive knowledge of the methods, programs and curriculums that lead to better results within the Saudi education system, as well as those that do not.\r\n \r\nBy combining our teams expertise with our unrivalled experience of delivering successful foundation programs here in Saudi Arabia, we are uniquely placed to provide stable, efficient, tried and tested excellence in academic management.', 'Academic Management Solutions', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1975-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-10 17:53:38', '2014-06-10 10:53:38', '', 1975, 'http://sfr-creative.com/1975-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
