(2119, 1, '2014-06-10 17:56:39', '2014-06-10 10:56:39', 'At ICEAT we are full engaged with the exciting opportunities for education offered by technology. As technology has developed and the eLearning industry has continued to grow, we believe the eLearning solutions have increasingly been able to offer powerful opportunities to enhance teaching and learning for all.\r\n\r\nThat is why we have embraced and become fully involved with the rapidly growing eLearning sector. Through the knowledge and experience of our partners MKCL, with their advanced eLearning solutions, through our utilization of Rosetta Stone’s industry leading expertise and software, or through our understanding of Pearson’s excellent eLearning support, we are invested heavily in the possibilities offered by eLearning. \r\n\r\nBy utilizing the power of technology, we at ICEAT believe we can empower teachers to teach, and learners to learn at their full potential. By blending autonomous, independent learning with face-to-face support, through technology, we aim to create a fully immersive, reactive learning environment.', 'E-Learning Solutions', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1967-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-10 17:56:39', '2014-06-10 10:56:39', '', 1967, 'http://sfr-creative.com/1967-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(2120, 1, '2014-06-10 17:57:22', '2014-06-10 10:57:22', 'Together with our national and international partners we work hard to combine best practices in the world of education with our clear understanding of local needs. In so doing we at ICEAT are continually striving to improve the world-class management solutions provided to our education and training clients in the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia.\r\n\r\nFrom our unparalleled human-resources systems and procedures to our performance management, our understanding of the detailed administrative demands of large-scale education providers, and our knowledge and experience delivering assessment eLearning and professional development solutions, we provide the very highest quality in education management.', 'Turnkey Solutions', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1973-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-06-10 17:57:22', '2014-06-10 10:57:22', '', 1973, 'http://sfr-creative.com/1973-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
